Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Có lẽ là...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mình đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thích cậu rồi!!
